flowchart TD
    A[Requesting Unit] --> B[Prepare Documents:<br/>- Service Request Form<br/>- Business Case*]
    B --> C{Unit Head<br/>Approval?}
    C -->|No| D[Return for Revision]
    C -->|Yes| E[Submit to DOTD Service Desk<br/> via Document Flow System]
    E --> F[DOTD Triage & Feasibility Check<br/> SLA: 3-5 days]

    F --> G{Request Type}
    G -->|Routine<br/> e.g., device fix, training| H[DOTD Department Head<br/>Approval]
    G -->|Major<br/> e.g., new software, infrastructure | I[General Director Review]

    H --> K[DOTD Execute<br/>Assign Project ID]
    I --> J{Cost > $10K or<br/>Cross-Unit Impact?}
    J -->|No| K
    J -->|Yes| L[Secretariat of State Review]
    L --> M{Ministry-Wide<br/>Impact?}
    M -->|No| K
    M -->|Yes| N[Deputy Minister Approval]
    N --> K

    K --> O[Track via:<br/>- Document Archive<br/>- Monthly Reports]
    O --> P[Closeout Report to Requesting Unit]
    P --> Q{Feedback<br/>Received?}
    Q -->|Yes| R[Update SOPs/Knowledge Base]
    Q -->|No| S[Auto-close after 7 days]

    classDef routine fill:#d4f7d4,stroke:#333
    classDef major fill:#ffe8c4,stroke:#333
    classDef exec fill:#c4d4ff,stroke:#333
    class G,H routine
    class I,J,L,M,N major
    class K,O,P exec